  "body": "Modifying the array directly in the loop body is disallowed, so this could be considered a bug:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nx: uint256[1]\r\n\r\n@private\r\ndef store_in_x(index: uint256, value: uint256):\r\n    self.x[index] = value\r\n\r\n@public\r\ndef foo():\r\n    for n in self.x:\r\n        # self.x[0] = n * 2 # blocked with \"Altering list 'self.x' which is being iterated!\"\r\n        self.store_in_x(0, n * 2) # BUG: allowed\r\n```",
